OL,5,
OL,6,CG1992FBlack in Blue airs on BBC One.
OL,7,
OL,8,FRadio Times: "The Metropolitan Police
OL,9,Fstill needs more black and Asian
OL,10,Fofficers. More than three years ago
OL,11,FDesmond Wilcox filmed the progress of
OL,12,Fseven such recruits - three men and
OL,13,Ffour women - through training and on to
OL,14,Fthe streets. But by the end of the
OL,15,Fseries, two had quit.
OL,16,
OL,17,F"Since then, one more has left the
OL,18,Fforce and those still serving have
OL,19,Flearned much about prejudice that
OL,20,Fshould be useful to their bosses. This
OL,21,Fprogramme provides an update on the
OL,22,Fprogress of those who stayed the
OL,23,Sppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
